Description.LocalizedString: A sentient AI who will stop at nothing to wipe out humanity.
A body built for destruction, warped by an all-consuming fire.
A sharp instrument attached to the arm, wrapped in tendrils of flesh.
A hyperconscious AI driven to kill by his hatred for humanity.
A body built for bloodshed, incinerated by an all-consuming fire.
A malicious instrument fused to the arm, held in place by tendrils of flesh.
A rugged engineer, cloned and raised to handle the unique problems of planetary colonization.
A lightweight, insulating vest that holds his many tools of the trade.
Safety gear worn while doing repairs in unstable environments.
A dogged engineer, prepared and determined to handle the unique problems of planetary colonization.
A filthy vest that does nothing to keep his tools clean.
Safety gear tainted while doing repairs in unstable environments.
A curved scrap-metal blade covered in rust and blood.
A shirt that reflects extra light for repair work in dark environments.
